<ns1666:section xmlns:ns1666="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.concepts.architecture.examples.cofLoader.generating.selectingModifiabilityTactics">

  <ns1667:title xmlns:ns1667="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Selecting modifiability tactics</ns1667:title>
  <ns1668:para xmlns:ns1668="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    The core strategies used for realizing modifiability are
    <ns1669:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1669="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      <ns1670:listitem xmlns:ns1670="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1671:para xmlns:ns1671="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">complexity reduction,</ns1671:para></ns1670:listitem>
      <ns1672:listitem xmlns:ns1672="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1673:para xmlns:ns1673="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">localized maintenance, and</ns1673:para></ns1672:listitem>
      <ns1674:listitem xmlns:ns1674="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1675:para xmlns:ns1675="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">late binding.</ns1675:para></ns1674:listitem>
    </ns1669:itemizedlist>
  </ns1668:para>
  
  <ns1676:section xmlns:ns1676="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    <ns1677:title xmlns:ns1677="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Complexity reduction</ns1677:title>
    <ns1678:para xmlns:ns1678="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      Tactics used to realize complexity reduction include
      <ns1679:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1679="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        <ns1680:listitem xmlns:ns1680="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1681:para xmlns:ns1681="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
          minimizing component complexity, and
        </ns1681:para></ns1680:listitem>
        <ns1682:listitem xmlns:ns1682="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1683:para xmlns:ns1683="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
          minimizing dependencies.
        </ns1683:para></ns1682:listitem>
      </ns1679:itemizedlist>
      We will try and employ both.
    </ns1678:para>
  </ns1676:section>
  
  <ns1684:section xmlns:ns1684="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    <ns1685:title xmlns:ns1685="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Localized maintenance</ns1685:title>
    <ns1686:para xmlns:ns1686="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      The tactics used to realize localized maintenance include
      <ns1687:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1687="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        <ns1688:listitem xmlns:ns1688="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1689:para xmlns:ns1689="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
          semantic coherence,
        </ns1689:para></ns1688:listitem>
        <ns1690:listitem xmlns:ns1690="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1691:para xmlns:ns1691="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
          encapsulation,
        </ns1691:para></ns1690:listitem>
        <ns1692:listitem xmlns:ns1692="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1693:para xmlns:ns1693="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
          decoupling, and
        </ns1693:para></ns1692:listitem>
        <ns1694:listitem xmlns:ns1694="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1695:para xmlns:ns1695="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
          generalization.
        </ns1695:para></ns1694:listitem>
      </ns1687:itemizedlist>
      Again, we will try and employ them all.        
    </ns1686:para>
  </ns1684:section>
  
  <ns1696:section xmlns:ns1696="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    <ns1697:title xmlns:ns1697="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Late binding</ns1697:title>
    <ns1698:para xmlns:ns1698="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      The tactics used to realize late binding include
      <ns1699:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1699="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        <ns1700:listitem xmlns:ns1700="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1701:para xmlns:ns1701="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">run-time registration,</ns1701:para></ns1700:listitem>
        <ns1702:listitem xmlns:ns1702="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1703:para xmlns:ns1703="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">configuration files, and</ns1703:para></ns1702:listitem>
        <ns1704:listitem xmlns:ns1704="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1705:para xmlns:ns1705="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">registering with naming/trader services.</ns1705:para></ns1704:listitem>
      </ns1699:itemizedlist>
      The process is meant to be a batch process with minimal user interface. To keep 
      complexity down we shall only use configuration files.
    </ns1698:para>
  </ns1696:section>
</ns1666:section>